However, without more context, it is unclear whether this lack of content is specific to the vehicle context or extends to the organizational context as well.

title: "AUTOMATICALLY"
description: "Automatically refers to a process that occurs without human intervention, in this case, the renewal of the STR budget."

title: "DELAYED STARTUP"
description: "The event Delayed Startup refers to the start of something being delayed."
